CatDescriptText: Exterior of Casey - Staisey, 21st. Ward reg. Democratic, Headquarters in the Hill District with Governor Casey standing next to his wife shaking hands with a local community member.  In the window are posters which read "Vote Casey Staisey, Governor Lt. Governor, to win in '6..."  A prominent car tail fin in the foreground belongs to a 1959 Oldsmobile.
TitMainTitle: Robert Casey, candidate for Pennsylvania governor, shaking hands outside Casey Staisey 21st Ward Democratic Headquarters, next door to A. M. Simon Scrap Iron and Steel, street no. 1226
